###Human: Build a landing page for a language learning platform targeting travelers. Design a dynamic hero section with a world map, language icons, and a headline highlighting the benefits of learning new languages. Incorporate sections showcasing popular language courses, learner success stories, and a call-to-action button for users to start their language journey. ###Assistant:<!DOCTYPE html>

