###Human: Develop a landing page for a pet adoption agency promoting animal adoptions. Create an adorable hero section with heartwarming pet images, a headline advocating pet adoption, and a search form for visitors to find their perfect furry companion. Include sections featuring available pets, adoption success stories, and a call-to-action to start the adoption process. ###Assistant:<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>
<head>
<style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #fafafa;
        }

        .hero {
            width: 100%;
            height: 70vh;
            background-image: url('');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            position: relative;
        }

        .headline {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 20%;
            left: 15%;
            color: white;
            font-size: 2.5em;
        }

        .searchForm {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 10%;
            left: 15%;
        }

        .searchForm input[type="text"] {
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 10px;
            width: 300px;
        }

        .section {
            padding: 5% 15%;
        }

        .section h2 {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 2em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .section img {
            width: 25%;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .cta {
            background-color: #fb8c00;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 5% 0;
        }

        .cta button {
            color: white;
            background-color: #f4511e;
            border: none;
            padding: 15px 32px;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="hero">
<h1 class="headline">Adopt, Don't Shop</h1>
<div class="searchForm">
<input placeholder="Find your perfect furry friend..." type="text"/>
<input type="submit" value="Search"/>
</div>
</div>
<div class="section">
<h2>Meet Our Adoptable Pets</h2>
<img alt="Pet Image" src="http://via.placeholder.com/640x360"/>
<img alt="Pet Image" src="http://via.placeholder.com/640x360"/>
<img alt="Pet Image" src="http://via.placeholder.com/640x360"/>
<img alt="Pet Image" src="http://via.placeholder.com/640x360"/>
</div>
<div class="section">
<h2>Adoption Success Stories</h2>
<img alt="Success Story Image" src="http://via.placeholder.com/640x360"/>
<img alt="Success Story Image" src="http://via.placeholder.com/640x360"/>
<img alt="Success Story Image" src="http://via.placeholder.com/640x360"/>
<img alt="Success Story Image" src="http://via.placeholder.com/640x360"/>
</div>
